Implement the private `compensate_all/3` function. It receives `completed` (the
list of already-succeeded step entries, in **reverse-execution order** — most
recent first), the accumulated `context`, and `jrev0` (the journal accumulated
so far in reverse order — most recent event first). It must run each completed
